{"id":249291,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/08/维权网-交通事故致残未处理反遭判刑，夫妻上访/","date":"2012-08-29T14:00:52Z","modified":"2012-08-29T14:00:52Z","title":"维权网 | 交通事故致残未处理反遭判刑，夫妻上访被拘留（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员周维林报道）安徽省涡阳县周建因交通事故致残，妻子张元荣因肇事方弃车逃逸，多次找交警大队查明肇事方，后因发生家庭内部冲突，导致周建被法院判刑，夫妻二人皆认定是遭警方报复构陷，故上访申诉，却屡遭警方拘留。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>据周建、张元荣反映，周建于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2008</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">26</span><span>日下午</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">14</span><span>时</span><span>骑摩托车与一三轮摩托车相撞头部受伤昏迷，送进医院抢救，昏迷了</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">15</span><span>天后苏醒，如今依然留有后遗症，丧失劳动能力；肇事方当时弃车逃逸，张元荣按警方通知到医院，其后到交警大队要求查找到肇事方，此后多次提供线索要警方查找，但警方放任肇事方将警方放到停车场的摩托车拿走，而不确认身份、抓获，更因此不出交通事故责任认定书，为此被张元荣、周建多次“缠访、闹访”，其后周建与父亲哥哥因宅基地问题发生矛盾、冲突，被涡阳县公安局于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>日</span><span>以涉嫌故意伤害罪逮捕，涡阳县人民法院判刑一年缓期一年执行，周建被关押长达</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>个多月。夫妻二人皆认为这是警方因他们上访而串通家人报复所致，故其后多次上访，又因上访屡遭拘留。近日再次到安徽省高级人民法院申请再审。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>周建、张元荣夫妻二人认为周建交通事故致残丧失劳动能力，因交警大队不作为，放纵肇事方逃脱，致使周建致残未获赔偿，却因上访反遭警方报复判刑，再因判刑而上访，并多次被拘留，如此不公，他们岂能放弃诉求，所以依旧坚持上访申诉，期待相关部门能依法公正处理。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-ICei7OhlG-I/UD4gKD7xE1I/AAAAAAAAMiM/GvE8LC05jUY/s1600/P1020584.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-ICei7OhlG-I/UD4gKD7xE1I/AAAAAAAAMiM/GvE8LC05jUY/s320/P1020584.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-PQKpj39r7ik/UD4f3vkZTxI/AAAAAAAAMh8/h1LYkKZaGyA/s1600/%E5%91%8A%E7%9F%A5%E5%91%A8%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%8D%E5%BE%97%E8%87%AA%E6%AE%8B%E4%B9%A6.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-PQKpj39r7ik/UD4f3vkZTxI/AAAAAAAAMh8/h1LYkKZaGyA/s320/%E5%91%8A%E7%9F%A5%E5%91%A8%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%8D%E5%BE%97%E8%87%AA%E6%AE%8B%E4%B9%A6.JPG\" width=\"240\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-dwAno4nkiIg/UD4f63qiS1I/AAAAAAAAMiE/GutkdTUl3do/s1600/%E5%BC%A0%E5%85%83%E8%8D%A3%E6%8B%98%E7%95%99%E5%86%B3%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%A6.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-dwAno4nkiIg/UD4f63qiS1I/AAAAAAAAMiE/GutkdTUl3do/s320/%E5%BC%A0%E5%85%83%E8%8D%A3%E6%8B%98%E7%95%99%E5%86%B3%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%A6.JPG\" width=\"240\" /></a></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n</div>\n<div><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/751033951089627103-6452276463345543260?l=wqw2010.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=2ea93c5b7b\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/msuvD\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18269,20534],"tags":[16910]}